<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5104030003">
<title>
DTC Confirmation Procedure
</title>
<attention1>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Perform road test in a place where there is no traffic to prevent an accident.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Road test should be performed with two persons, a driver and a tester, on a level road.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Warm up engine to normal operating temperature.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drive vehicle at more than 50 km/h (31 mile/h) in “D” range for 3 min.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5104030004">
<title>
DTC Troubleshooting
</title>
<diag type = "test" id = "AENAP70B5104030005">
<testgroup id = "AENAP70B5104030006">
<question>
Was “A/T Control System Check” performed?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 2.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B5104001">A/T Control System Check</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70B5104030007">
<title>
Output shaft speed sensor power supply circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition “OFF” and disconnect connector from output shaft speed sensor.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check for proper terminal connection to output shaft speed sensor connector.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
If connections are OK, set ignition “ON”.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check that voltage between output shaft speed sensor power supply circuit (A1) and ground is battery voltage.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 3.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70B5104030008">
<title>
Output shaft speed sensor ground circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check that voltage between output shaft speed sensor power supply circuit (A1) and ground circuit (A3) is battery voltage.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 4.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70B5104030009">
<title>
Output shaft speed sensor signal circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition “OFF” and disconnect connectors from TCM.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check for proper terminal connection to TCM connectors.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
If connections are OK, check that output shaft speed sensor signal circuit (A2) is as follows.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Wiring harness resistance of output shaft speed sensor signal circuit is less than 1 Ω.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Insulation resistance between output shaft speed sensor signal circuit and ground is infinity.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Insulation resistance of wire harness is infinity between output shaft speed sensor signal circuit terminal and each terminal at output shaft speed sensor connector.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Circuit voltage of output shaft speed sensor signal circuit is approx. 0 V with ignition “ON”.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 5.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70B5104030010">
<title>
Output shaft speed sensor check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check output shaft speed sensor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106019"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 6.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace output shaft speed sensor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106018"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70B5104030011">
<title>
Output shaft speed sensor gears visual check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check output shaft speed sensor gears visually as follows.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
No damage in drive gear on differential case
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
No damage in driven gear in output shaft speed sensor
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Is result satisfactory?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Substitute a known-good TCM and recheck DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106030"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace drive gear and/or output shaft speed sensor.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
</diag>
